name: Transportadora Bracco
description: A transportadora Bracco Travel 2 é projetada para viagens seguras com animais, cumprindo normas IATA. É feita de plástico durável, com ventilação e porta de metal, perfeita para o transporte aéreo e terrestre.
descricao: TRANSPORTER LOTNICZY DLA PSA KOTA Z ATESTEM LOTNICZYM IATA  MP BERGAMO BRACCO TRAVEL 2   55 x 36 x 35 cm .  Solidny, plastikowy transporter do przewozu małego psa lub kota w samochodzie, pociągu lub samolotem. . Profesjonalny transporter dla zwierząt akceptowany przez większość międzynarodowych linii lotniczych. Podczas transportu naszych pupili należy zagwarantować im bezpieczeństwo oraz wygodę i komfort, aby zmniejszyć stres związany z podróżą. Transporter lotniczy BRACCO TRAVEL został stworzony z myślą o zwierzętach często podróżujących ze swoimi właścicielami między innymi samolotem i dostosowany, aby spełniać wszelkie normy przewozu zwierząt w pasażerskim transporcie lotniczym. Starannie wykonane transportery do przewozu psów BRACCO pozwalają zwierzęciu na udział we wszelkiego typu podróżach (samochodem, pociągiem, samolotem). Są wytrzymałe i łatwo je utrzymać w czystości. Zapewniają bezpieczeństwo podróżującemu zwierzęciu oraz innym pasażerom dzięki solidnym metalowym drzwiczkom z metalowymi bolcami z blokadą zamka. Transporter BRACCO 2 posiada otwory wentylacyjne z każdej ze stron. Transporter Bracco 2 wyposażono w mocowania pasa samochodowego oraz zaczepy do paska na ramie. W zestawie znajduje się również miska na wodę montowana na drzwiach transportera. Transportery BRACCO zostały wyposażone w 2 rączki do noszenia. Przednia rączka służy również do ciągnięcia transportera po zamontowaniu dedykowanych kółek. Transporter bardzo łatwo złożyć oraz wyczyścić. Widoczne na zdjęciach śruby nie są dołączone do zestawu, można zakupić je osobno z naszej oferty.  Ważne informacje przed podróżą lotniczą: . Produkt ten został stworzony zgodnie z aktualnymi wytycznymi IATA (Międzynarodowe Zrzeszenie Przewoźników Powietrznych), jednak to linie lotnicze decydują czy dany transporter będzie akceptowany w ich samolocie. Przed zakupem należy zadzwonić do przewoźnika oraz podając model oraz wymiary dopytać czy transporter spełnia ich wymogi. Dodatkowo linie lotnicze zwracają uwagę na odpowiednie dobranie rozmiarów klatki do wymiarów psa. Zgodnie z wytycznymi IATA pies w klatce powinien móc w pełni się wyprostować, obrócić oraz położyć w pozycji naturalnej. Odpowiednie wymiary klatki to. Wysokość: wysokość psa/kota podczas stania mierzona od ziemi aż po czubek głowy lub czubek uszu. Szerokość: 2 x szerokość psa/kota mierzona na wysokości łopatek. Długość: długość psa mierzona od nosa aż po ogon + połowa długości przednich łap. Zwierzę można też zmierzyć jak leży w pozycji naturalnej.  Dane techniczne: . Wymiary zewnętrze: 55x36x35cm. Rekomendowany ciężar zwierzęcia: 8-10kg. Waga transportera: 1,8kg.

O equilíbrio dos microrganismos é importante para te r um efeito positivo na saúde digestiva, no sistema imunitário e no bem-estar geral do seu gato. PURINA ONE® BIFENSIS® é uma fórmula nutricional com uma bactéria benéfica funcional: Lactobacillus, cientificamente comprovado para fortalecer o sistema imuni tário do seu gato de dentro para fora e ajudar a proteger um microbioma intestinal saudável. Contém ingredientes de elevada qualidade, incluindo prebiótico: chicória, que nutre bactérias boas no intestino para melhorar o microbioma intestinal do seu gato para o manter saudável. Desde uma digestão saudável e um sistema imunitário forte a um pelo brilhante, pode ver resultados visíveis na saúde do seu gato hoje e amanhã.

name: Gelado Cone Clássico
descricao: Cornetto Classico Ice Cream Cone is made up of a delicious, crispy-baked wafer cone, coated inside from top to bottom with a chocolate layer, combined with smooth vanilla flavour ice cream and topped with tasty hazelnut. For over 50 years we’ve been perfecting our Cornetto recipe, making sure the taste of every Cornetto ice cream is better than the last. Taking your taste buds on a delicious journey from the tasty hazelnut topping, through the smooth vanilla ice cream, down to the crunchy wafer cone – and of course, ending with the legendary chocolatey tip. An Italian ice cream manufacturer from Naples was passionate about ice cream, loving smooth texture, delicious flavours and great ingredients. One day, they found a way to spread their passion for ice cream to everyone. The great idea was to cover the inside of the cone with a chocolatey layer, allowing the wafer to keep its crispiness when filled with ice cream. From this breakthrough, we have the Cornetto we know and love today.

name: Portal da Calçada Loureiro Alvarinho DOC Vinho Verde Branco
description: Mundus Vini 20232023: Medalha de Ouro
descricao: Der Portal da Calada Reserva ist eine ausgewogene,trockene Weiwein-Cuve und ein klassischer Vinho Verde, das heit der grne Wein aus dem Norden Portugals. Er hat einen geschmacksintensiven Ausdruck. Genieen Sie die schnen floralen und fruchtigen Noten mit Birnen- und Melonenaromen. Die Vinho Verde zeichnen sich aus, durch ihr spritziges, unbeschwertes Wesen und den geringen Alkoholgehalt, welshalb sie sich grter Beliebtheit erfreuen. Tolle Weine fr jeden Anlass! Unsere Lieblingsbloggerin Astrid Paul empfiehlt in Ihrem Blog diesen ausgewogenen Wein zurEndiviensuppe mit sous vide gegarten Kartoffel-Wrfeln, roter Zwiebel, Radieschen! Die Quinta da Calada wurde im Jahr 1917, imHerzen des Stdtchens Amarante, in der gleichnamigenRegion des Vinho Verde Gebietes gebaut. Die berhmteste portugiesische Weiweinregion. Bis heute ist das Weingut in Familienbesitz, die es mit flammendem Ehrgeiz leitet. Die historischen Gebude beherbergenauch ein feines Relais&Chteaux Hotel sowie dasSpitzenrestaurant Largo do Pao. Die Region Amarante ist genau von den Bdengeprgt, die zu besonders feinen Vinho VerdeWeinen fhren. Granitverwitterungsgestein, hierund da mit Schieferauflagen, dazu bestens angepassteheimische Rebsorten und khlende Einflsse vomnahen Atlantik: so erhalten die Weine genau dieanimierende Mineralitt, fr die sie weltberhmtsind. Die Reserva Portal da Calada hat uns totalbegeistert!

A wet and dry vacuum cleaner provides good service for the careful cleaning of surfaces that are not sensitive to water. For household work, for carpets or fixed textiles, tiles or all types of glazed tiles with open pores, normal surface cleaning alone is often not enough. A wet & dry vac can also be used for cleaning the insides of all kinds of vehicles, right to the tips of the textile material, be it seats and roof linings or mats and interior trim. The wet & dry vac from Einhell is equipped with a rust-proof and sturdy stainless steel tank with a capacity of 20 liters. The hose system with a diameter of 36 mm maintains high air and dirt flow. The blow connection is for blow-cleaning hard-to-reach areas such as in awkward corners or behind solid cupboards. For easy transport and flexibility in use there are castors. For tidiness during use there is a practical accessories holder and a cable holder on the housing. description: Prémios Uva de Ouro 2021: Medalha de Prata
descricao: Vinho de origem portuguesa, produzido com uvas brancas européias - verdelho (64%), viosinho (14%), viognier (22%). apresenta coloração amarelo citrino, aroma frutado destacanto lima, manga e banana, com toques de flor de laranjeira. o paladar observa corpo médio com sabor frutado e acidez equilibrada. vinificação: fermentado em depósito deinox a 16ºc. conservação em cave: as garrafasdeitadas a uma temperatura ambiente de12ºc e humidade de 60% notas de prova: cor: amarelo limonadoaroma: damasco, melão, abacaxi, manga,mineralpaladar: suave, delicado, boa fruta com boaacidezfinal de prova: médioharmonização: como aperitivo ou acompanhamento de peixe oumariscoscomoaperitivo ou acompanhamento de peixe oumariscos. temperatura de consumo: 11° a 12ºclongevidade prevista: beber enquantojovem graduação alcoólica: 12,5% vol. historia: ovinho periquitaé conhecido como o primeirovinho tintoengarrafado em portugal. essa inovação traduz a sua originalidade e, o reflexo da portugalidade surge da sua presença na mesa dos portugueses – de todos nós – desde 1850. à nossa, ao estilo de vida português! a história do periquita remonta ao início da própria história da josé maria da fonseca, quando o fundador da empresa, o senhor josé maria da fonseca comprou, por volta de 1846, a propriedade cova da periquita. foi nessa propriedade, hoje em dia quase engolida pelo desenvolvimento urbano, que josé maria da fonseca plantou as primeiras uvas da casta castelão, que ele próprio havia trazido, muito provavelmente, da província do ribatejo. o vinho produzido na cova da periquita desde logo provou ser o melhor da região dando origem a que os outros proprietários pedissem a josé maria da fonseca varas daquela casta para plantarem nas suas próprias propriedades. desta forma, o vinho tornou-se conhecido em azeitão como o vinho da periquita, passando a ser comercializado pela josé maria da fonseca como periquita. embora não possa ser avançada com exactidão a data em que a primeira colheita foi produzida, é porém certo que o periquita já estava a ser produzido em 1850, tendo a colheita de 1886 recebido a medalha de ouro na exposição de vinhos de berlim em 1888. josé maria da fonseca registou a marca periquita em 1941. por este motivo, o periquita é na actualidade a mais antiga marca portuguesa de vinho de mesa comercializada tendo adquirido, ao longo do tempo, uma crescente popularidade em portugal e uma considerável notoriedade em mercados tais como a suécia, o brasil, reino unido, estados unidos da américa, canadá, dinamarca e noruega.

name: Croft DOC Vinho do Porto LBV
description:
Prémios Uva de Ouro 2023: Medalha de Ouro


Croft, uma das casas de Vinho do Porto mais ilustres!
descricao: Tasting Notes Croft was established in 1588 making it the oldest Port House still in operation. Their wines have therefore become dinner party and festive season classics throughout the world. The Late Bottle Vintage 2013 is like blackcurrant coulis prunes rose petals Russian Caravan tea chocolate-covered almonds herby balsamic coffee and Christmas cake all trapped beneath a cork. LBVs are aged for longer in wood so that when bottled they're ready to drink immediately. So crack this open with cheese chocolate-based desserts and festive fare or simply sip it after dinner next to the fireplace. The Croft story begins unexpectedly in York. Henry Thomson began trading wine in the city in 1588. War with France caused the Thompsons to refocus their business on Portugal and the family later married into the Croft's family a century later giving birth to Croft Port as we know it today. The family-run business owns immaculate terraced vineyards throughout the region including Quinta da Roda one of the Douro Valley's star vineyards. Their approach a juxtaposition of tradition and innovation; still employing foot stomping in the winery but also being first to create a ros Port. name: Dona Ermelinda DOC Palmela Vinho Rosé

"O solo destas vinhas é composto por areias muito semelhantes às areias de praia e muit o rico em água, desempenhando um papel importante na maturação das uvas. A brisa envolvente dos rios refresca as vinhas durante os verões secos, atribuindo suavidade e elegância aos vinhos. É nestes solos arenosos que prospera o Castelão." Hoje a Casa E rmelinda Freitas tem um total de 30 castas diferentes, que são exploradas anualmente nas suas terras.

name: Gin Sharish Blue
descricao: Distilled in a traditional portuguese copper still it uses a combination of 9 botanicals carefully selected. Due to the different characteristics and points of evaporation, the botanicals slowly distillate separately, allowing a greater quality in the final distillation. During the process, all the impurities are removed so the result is as limpid as possible. A bright blue Portuguese gin from the Sharish range - the magnificent colour comes from extracts of a flower known as blue pea, and when you mix the gin with tonic, it turns pink! A combination of 9 botanicals carefully selected: Juniper, Cinnamon, Coriander seeds, Clove, Vanilla, Orange Peel, Lemon Peel, Bravo Esmolfe Apple PDO (Protected designation of origin) and Lemon verbena. With the particularity that the last four botanicals are used fresh. A new portuguese gin produced in Alentejo by Antonio Cuco gets its name because of the village MONSARAZ. Sharish means 'xara' or 'jara', which is the Cistus ladanifer, used during the muslim presence. So Mont Sharish means hill raised in an impenetrable amount of cistus, giving origin to the name Monsaraz. Mix this gin with tonic, it turns pink!

name: Champanhe Taittinger Prestige Bruto Rosé
descricao: Taittinger, established in 1734, is a prestigious champagne house celebrated for its dedication to quality and tradition. With a legacy of craftsmanship and excellence, Taittinger produces champagnes that are the epitome of refinement. The brand is renowned for its elegant style and adherence to traditional methods, ensuring that each bottle embodies the artistry and heritage of fine champagne making.Taittinger Prestige Rosé NV Champagne is a refined and elegant rosé champagne that captures the essence of sophistication. This 75 cl bottle is crafted from a blend of Pinot Noir and Chardonnay grapes, delivering a delicate yet vibrant profile. The champagne features a beautiful salmon-pink hue and a fine, persistent mousse. Ideal for special occasions or as an aperitif, the Taittinger Prestige Rosé NV combines freshness with a hint of fruitiness, making it a versatile choice for any celebration.The Taittinger Prestige Rosé NV Champagne offers a delightful bouquet of red berries, including strawberry and raspberry, complemented by subtle notes of rose petals and citrus zest. On the palate, it presents a harmonious balance of fresh fruit flavors and a hint of spice. The champagnes texture is smooth and creamy, with a lively effervescence and a crisp, elegant finish. It pairs beautifully with fresh seafood, grilled vegetables, and fruit-based desserts, making it a versatile and enjoyable choice for any occasion.

name: Gin Ginraw
descricao: The nose offers an excellent aromatic intensity, essentially fresh with crispy citrus and floral notes and green tips of the combination of lemon, citron and kaffir lime leaf. Ginraw is made in small batches to ensure the excellence of quality and taste in each bottle. Elegant with delightful citrus notes.

name: Água Tónica Elderflower
descricao: By blending the essential oils from handpicked English elderflowers with quinine of the highest quality from the 'fever trees' of the Democratic Republic of the Congo, we have created a delicious, floral variation of our Indian tonic water.
